data.description: CHECK THIS HOME OUT!! Established neighorhood with nice large trees. An AWESOME find! This home offers 3 pretty big bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Primary BR downstairs. Large closets. Each room is spacious. Easily accessible to Hwy 75 that offers dining, shopping, schools, and even WATERLOO PARK with walking trails. Home is updated with paint, carpet, fixtures, and even the roof is less than a year old. 2 car garage plus tandem corner area for extra storage. Extended driveway allows for additional parking for RV or boat.  Great open back yard. This home is clean and ready to be seen! Reach out for SPECIAL DEAL!
